PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology of Jocelyne Bourgon as a director of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Georgina Wyman, whose term has expired; and designation of the said Jocelyne Bourgon as a director of the Executive Committee of the Federal Business Development Bank.
Attachments
precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry, Science and
Technology of Jocelyne Bourgon as a director of the Board of Directors of
the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for
a term of three years, in the place of Georgina Wyman, whose term has
expired; and designation of the said Jocelyne Bourgon as a director of
the Executive Committee of the Federal Business Development Bank.
